<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 20:06:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国家将向在加沙战斗中丧生的菲律宾裔以色列国防军士兵的父母授予公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/state-to-grant-citizenship-to-parents-of-filipino-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-5189-d5c3-a9fd-75ddded40000</link><description>西德里克·加林 (Cydrick Garin) 和其他 20 名士兵在加沙的一座建筑倒塌中丧生。他的父母是来自菲律宾的民工，他的父亲在他出生后就被驱逐出境。他的母亲说：“他是菲律宾公民，但他将一生奉献给了他深爱的祖国以色列”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 20:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/state-to-grant-citizenship-to-parents-of-filipino-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-5189-d5c3-a9fd-75ddded40000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟主席错误地暗示奥斯威辛集中营是波兰而非德国，引发波兰抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/eu-chief-erroneously-suggests-auschwitz-was-polish-not-german-sparking-protest-in-poland/0000018d-511e-d3ab-a5cf-539f2b7d0000</link><description>欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩随后发表帖子澄清奥斯威辛是纳粹德国的灭绝营。近年来，波兰严厉打击了公众对其在大屠杀中所扮演角色的批评</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 19:59:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/eu-chief-erroneously-suggests-auschwitz-was-polish-not-german-sparking-protest-in-poland/0000018d-511e-d3ab-a5cf-539f2b7d0000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处充斥着哈马斯。但以色列别无选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-is-riddled-with-hamas-but-israel-has-no-alternative/0000018d-5122-d3ab-a5cf-53bf4b370000</link><description>在近东救济工程处难民机构的一些成员参与了 10 月 7 日的大屠杀后，西方国家政府可能已经冻结了向近东救济工程处难民机构支付的款项。然而，像以色列一样，他们知道帮助加沙地带的巴勒斯坦人至关重要</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 19:37:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-is-riddled-with-hamas-but-israel-has-no-alternative/0000018d-5122-d3ab-a5cf-53bf4b370000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦歌手参加当地比赛后，冰岛成为早期欧洲歌唱大赛的热门人选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/iceland-becomes-early-eurovision-favorite-after-palestinian-singer-enters-local-contest/0000018d-50ec-d3f3-a5ff-53fd5e840000</link><description>巴沙尔·穆拉德 (Bashar Murad) 将于五月与其他九首冰岛歌曲竞争，代表北欧国家参赛。与此同时，卢森堡选择以色列裔卢森堡人塔利·戈勒甘特(Tali Golergant)作为其官方代表</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 18:01:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/iceland-becomes-early-eurovision-favorite-after-palestinian-singer-enters-local-contest/0000018d-50ec-d3f3-a5ff-53fd5e840000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政党部长与数千名以色列人一起参加“重新安置加沙”会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/ministers-from-netanyahus-party-join-thousands-of-israelis-at-resettle-gaza-conference/0000018d-512f-dfdc-a5ad-db7f35e10000</link><description>以色列极右翼国家安全部长表示，“我们需要找到一种合法的方式让[巴勒斯坦人]自愿移民”；以色列反对派领导人对会议进行了猛烈抨击：“这破坏了一项潜在的协议，并危及以色列国防军士兵”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 17:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/ministers-from-netanyahus-party-join-thousands-of-israelis-at-resettle-gaza-conference/0000018d-512f-dfdc-a5ad-db7f35e10000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处表示，在调查完成之前不会处理 10 月 7 日针对员工的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-says-it-will-not-address-employees-oct-7-allegations-prior-to-probes-completion/0000018d-507e-d12b-afcd-d0feef570000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯办公室猛烈抨击九个国家停止向近东救济工程处提供资金的决定，称以色列针对近东救济工程处的行动是为了“消除巴勒斯坦难民问题”；近东救济工程处发言人表示，只能在下个月之前在加沙提供服务</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 16:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/unrwa-says-it-will-not-address-employees-oct-7-allegations-prior-to-probes-completion/0000018d-507e-d12b-afcd-d0feef570000</guid></item><item><title>在强烈反对下，数百名学者集会支持领导哈佛大学反犹太主义工作组的犹太研究学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/academics-rally-behind-jewish-studies-scholar-heading-harvards-antisemitism-task-force/0000018d-5086-d3f3-a5ff-53d739d20000</link><description>超过 300 名研究犹太历史、以色列社会、反犹太主义和大屠杀的学者表示，德里克·彭斯拉教授 (Derek Penslar) 是担任美国大学新工作组联合主席的理想人选，并认为针对他的反犹太主义指控是荒谬的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 15:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/academics-rally-behind-jewish-studies-scholar-heading-harvards-antisemitism-task-force/0000018d-5086-d3f3-a5ff-53d739d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队阻止抗议者阻止人道主义援助进入加沙地带</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-prevents-protesters-from-blocking-humanitarian-aid-entry-into-gaza-strip/0000018d-5073-dfdc-a5ad-da7f10990000</link><description>一名抗议者说，“战争时期你不能援助敌人，加沙人也是敌人的一部分。”以色列国防军部署了路障，并宣布穿越边境为军事禁区，以阻止右翼抗议者阻挡救援卡车进入</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 15:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-prevents-protesters-from-blocking-humanitarian-aid-entry-into-gaza-strip/0000018d-5073-dfdc-a5ad-da7f10990000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗向太空发射三颗卫星，标志着随着中东紧张局势加剧，其能力有所增强</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/iran-launches-three-satellites-into-space-showing-increased-capabilities-as-tensions-rise/0000018d-508d-dfdc-a5ad-daff4c490000</link><description>伊朗崭露头角的太空计划受到了西方的批评，一些人表示，在以色列-加沙战争和代理人势力的参与导致局势日益不稳定的情况下，这“缩短了伊朗伊斯兰共和国开发洲际弹道导弹的时间表”</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 15:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/iran-launches-three-satellites-into-space-showing-increased-capabilities-as-tensions-rise/0000018d-508d-dfdc-a5ad-daff4c490000</guid></item><item><title>报告：加沙地带 80% 的隧道网络仍然完好无损</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/report-80-percent-of-gaza-strips-tunnel-network-still-intact/0000018d-4fab-d35c-a39f-effbcb0a0000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，以色列仅摧毁了哈马斯在加沙的隧道基础设施的 20% 至 40%，由于对人质福利的担忧，以色列的行动进展缓慢</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 12:43:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/report-80-percent-of-gaza-strips-tunnel-network-still-intact/0000018d-4fab-d35c-a39f-effbcb0a0000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，以色列声称国际法院的部分命令已经生效</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-claim-some-of-icjs-orders-already-in-place-officials-say/0000018d-4f20-d35c-a39f-ef7aa0df0000</link><description>根据国际法院作出的初步裁决，以色列官员将被要求确保援助物资进入加沙，尽管边境有抗议活动，并对那些煽动种族灭绝的人进行起诉</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 11:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-claim-some-of-icjs-orders-already-in-place-officials-say/0000018d-4f20-d35c-a39f-ef7aa0df0000</guid></item><item><title>听：以色列军国主义热门歌曲敦促军队轰炸加沙，威胁贝拉·哈迪德和杜阿·利帕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-militaristic-hit-song-urges-troops-to-bomb-gaza-threatens-bella-hadid-dua-lipa/0000018d-4172-d02c-a79f-43fb0c920000</link><description>嘻哈二人组 Ness 和 Stilla 的“Harbu Darbu”与其说鼓励巴勒斯坦人的死亡，不如说它忽视了以色列人的死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 10:27:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-militaristic-hit-song-urges-troops-to-bomb-gaza-threatens-bella-hadid-dua-lipa/0000018d-4172-d02c-a79f-43fb0c920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称与美国、卡塔尔和埃及就哈马斯人质协议举行的峰会“具有建设性”；内塔尼亚胡：差距依然存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-live/following-icj-ruling-israel-to-forbid-protesters-to-block-aid-trucks-from-entering-gaza/0000018d-4e2a-d02c-a79f-4fbb2e6d0000</link><description>包括以色列部长在内的数千人参加耶路撒冷会议，要求重新安置加沙地带 ■ 无人机袭击约旦基地，造成 3 名美国士兵死亡、25 人受伤，这是加沙战争以来美军首次在中东丧生 ■ 美国称政策不会改变■ 报告：80% 的加沙隧道完好无损 ■ 美国高级官员：潜在的人质释放协议正在取得进展 ■ 八个国家停止向近东救济工程处提供资金，因为有指控称 12 名员工参与了以色列的哈马斯大屠杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 04:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article-live/following-icj-ruling-israel-to-forbid-protesters-to-block-aid-trucks-from-entering-gaza/0000018d-4e2a-d02c-a79f-4fbb2e6d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在人质协议峰会前加大对哈马斯的军事压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/ahead-of-hostage-summit-idf-presses-in-khan-yunis-and-engages-in-tunnel-warfare/0000018d-4c91-d35c-a39f-eedb64220000</link><description>对汗尤尼斯的包围已经完成，该市数万名居民在以色列的压力下逃离。与此同时，内塔尼亚胡政府的疯狂行为的证据不断堆积</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/ahead-of-hostage-summit-idf-presses-in-khan-yunis-and-engages-in-tunnel-warfare/0000018d-4c91-d35c-a39f-eedb64220000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡给以色列沉重打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dealt-israel-a-terrible-blow/0000018d-4c5b-d35c-a39f-ee5bdf4e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡并没有像他在第一本书《国际间的地位》中所承诺的那样，加强以色列在国际社会中的地位，而是将其带入了一个犯罪和杀人国家的地位</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 01:16:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dealt-israel-a-terrible-blow/0000018d-4c5b-d35c-a39f-ee5bdf4e0000</guid></item><item><title>抗议者在集会上援引大屠杀，要求释放被扣押在加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/protesters-invoke-holocaust-in-rallies-for-the-release-of-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018d-4cbe-d35c-a39f-eefe02710000</link><description>一千多名抗议者，其中包括被哈马斯在加沙扣押的人质的亲属，在特拉维夫所谓的人质广场和凯撒利亚总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的私人官邸外集会，要求立即释放人质</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 23:28:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-28/ty-article/.premium/protesters-invoke-holocaust-in-rallies-for-the-release-of-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018d-4cbe-d35c-a39f-eefe02710000</guid></item><item><title>“我伴侣的死是对政府及其领导人的起诉”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/my-partners-death-is-an-indictment-against-the-government-and-its-leader/0000018d-4c71-d02c-a79f-4ffb02c50000</link><description>特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法都举行了推翻内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议活动，贝尔谢巴也是自 10 月加沙战争爆发以来首次举行抗议活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 20:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/my-partners-death-is-an-indictment-against-the-government-and-its-leader/0000018d-4c71-d02c-a79f-4ffb02c50000</guid></item><item><title>挑衅的国际法院法官称以色列与加沙战争是“政治性的”，在世界法院没有地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/defiant-icj-judge-says-gaza-war-with-israel-is-political-and-has-no-place-in-world-court/0000018d-4ba5-d561-a5bd-6faff0060000</link><description>法官朱莉娅·塞布廷德在提交给联合国最高法院的少数意见中表示，“南非没有证明”以色列在加沙的行为“具有必要的种族灭绝意图”，因此符合《种族灭绝公约》的规定</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 17:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/defiant-icj-judge-says-gaza-war-with-israel-is-political-and-has-no-place-in-world-court/0000018d-4ba5-d561-a5bd-6faff0060000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯坚持结束战争，以色列官员对人质协议持悲观态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-pessimistic-about-hostage-deal-as-hamas-insists-on-end-to-war/0000018d-4baf-d561-a5bd-6faf1cf60000</link><description>哈马斯要求以色列完全撤军、国际社会保证结束战斗以及该组织重新控制加沙，这些都对达成协议构成了障碍。以色列高级官员表示，“就以色列而言，不可能为谈判创造一个起点”</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 17:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-pessimistic-about-hostage-deal-as-hamas-insists-on-end-to-war/0000018d-4baf-d561-a5bd-6faf1cf60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法律专家表示，国际法院法官基本上采纳了南非的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-legal-experts-say-icj-judges-largely-adopted-south-africas-narrative/0000018d-4bb7-d02c-a79f-4bbf16f60000</link><description>以色列人认为海牙法院没有成功下令停止加沙战争，但法院同意存在合理的种族灭绝风险</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jan 2024 16:50:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-legal-experts-say-icj-judges-largely-adopted-south-africas-narrative/0000018d-4bb7-d02c-a79f-4bbf16f60000</guid></item></channel></rss>